<task id="task-9900" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Finishing the Repair</title><shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc "/><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><context class="- topic/section task/context "/><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Tie a knot close to the fabric surface.
</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Insert the needle through the fabric and bring it out at another location.
